cef is provided as an unofficial CMake package:

  find_package(unofficial-cef CONFIG REQUIRED)
  target_link_libraries(your_target PRIVATE unofficial::cef::libcef)

At runtime, deploy:

Mandatory:
- <vcpkg>/installed/<triplet>/bin:
  libcef.dll, vulkan-1.dll, vk_swiftshader.dll, vk_swiftshader_icd.json, v8_context_snapshot.bin
- <vcpkg>/installed/<triplet>/share/cef/Resources

Optional (kept out of bin to avoid DLL name collisions with other ports):
- <vcpkg>/installed/<triplet>/share/cef/redist/Release
- <vcpkg>/installed/<triplet>/share/cef/redist/Debug

The CMake package also exposes:
- unofficial_cef_resources_dir
- unofficial_cef_redist_release_dir
- unofficial_cef_redist_debug_dir
